title: 5/9 - HR 2 - Draft Perspective, News Du Nord Donaldson Daily Digs Style
description: Nordo into hour 2 takes a retroactive peak back at the 2019 drafts going over which of those players are and are not having their 5th year team options picked up... The list may surprise you and is eye opening when it comes to forming opinions on draft night. Plus, the Daily Digs.
